 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering
							

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.017001152038574

===========

							 ORDER BY  ordering ASC,name ASC

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%3%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1

						 LIMIT 10

						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						FROM fs_blocks AS a 
						WHERE published = 1 
					ORDER BY ordering

					  FROM fs_products_categories
					  WHERE published = 1 AND is_special = 1

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering
							

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.002000093460083

===========

							FROM fs_manufactories

							 ORDER BY  ordering ASC,name ASC

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%4%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.00099992752075195

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering
							

time:::0

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.0010001659393311

===========

							 ORDER BY  ordering ASC,name ASC

						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%4%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0

						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%2%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT name,id,category_id,type,image,flash,content,link,height,width
						  FROM fs_banners AS a
						  WHERE published = 1
						  AND category_id IN (43) AND (listItemid = 'all'
							OR listItemid like '%,1,%')
							 ORDER BY ordering, id

						 LIMIT 4

					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						FROM fs_blocks AS a

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering
							

time:::0.0010008811950684

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.0019998550415039

===========

 SELECT id,name, image, alias
							FROM fs_manufactories 
							WHERE published = 1  
							 AND tablenames like "%,fs_products_tai_nghe,%"
							 ORDER BY  ordering ASC,name ASC

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%2%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

				WHERE module = "news" AND view = "home" AND ( task = "display" OR task = "" OR task IS NULL)

SELECT id,title,content, ordering, module, position, showTitle, params ,listItemid,news_categories,contents_categories,link_title
						FROM fs_blocks AS a 
						WHERE published = 1 
					ORDER BY ordering

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

 SELECT id,title,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,comments_total,comments_published FROM fs_news
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1
						  	 ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC 
						  LIMIT 0,10 

time:::0

===========

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_news
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1
						  	 ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC 
						 

time:::0.00099992752075195

SELECT name,alias,id,level,parent_id as parent_id,alias, list_parents,tablename,image,icon,show_in_homepage,show_in_footer						  FROM fs_products_categories AS a						  WHERE published = 1 						  ORDER BY ordering ASC, id ASC

 SELECT *						FROM fs_products_filters						WHERE published = 1						ORDER BY field_ordering ASC, ordering, is_common DESC

					FROM fs_menus_items
					WHERE published  = 1
						AND group_id = 1 
					ORDER BY ordering

						  FROM fs_news_categories AS a
						  WHERE published = 1
						  ORDER BY ordering ASC, id ASC

 SELECT id,link, name, alias, level, parent_id as parent_id, target,group_id, description,icon,image,show_filter
				FROM fs_menus_items
				WHERE published  = 1 AND group_id = 17
					ORDER BY ordering

time:::0.00099992752075195

 SELECT title,alias,image,summary,hits,updated_time,id,category_alias,is_hot,comments_total,created_time
						  FROM fs_news
						 WHERE  published = 1 and category_published = 1 
						  ORDER BY   ordering DESC,created_time DESC, ordering DESC,created_time DESC
						 LIMIT 6  
						 

time:::0.00099992752075195

					ORDER BY ordering

 SELECT id, name, level, alias,is_bold,link
					FROM fs_tags
					WHERE published  = 1  
					ORDER BY ordering
					LIMIT 150
